!-- -->Cap Congo, Lubunga</div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"opacity:0\"><img alt=\"Don de vareuses à la population de Lubunga\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fcolothes.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fcolothes.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fcolothes.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fcolothes.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fcolothes.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fcolothes.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fcolothes.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fcolothes.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fcolothes.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-cap-ink/90 via-cap-ink/40 to-transparent \n                md:bg-gradient-to-r md:from-cap-ink/90 md:via-cap-ink/50 md:to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-6 font-sans text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-white/70 \n                right-6 md:right-12\">Crédit photo © <!-- -->Cap Congo Agro Palm, Lubunga</div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"opacity:0\"><img alt=\"Distribution de maïs à Mushie Pentane\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Ffood_1.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Ffood_1.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Ffood_1.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Ffood_1.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Ffood_1.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Ffood_1.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Ffood_1.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Ffood_1.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Ffood_1.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-cap-ink/90 via-cap-ink/40 to-transparent \n                md:bg-gradient-to-l md:from-cap-ink/90 md:via-cap-ink/50 md:to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-6 font-sans text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-white/70 \n                left-6 md:left-12\">Crédit photo © <!-- -->Cap Congo Agricole Bandundu, Mushie Pentane</div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"opacity:0\"><img alt=\"Visite de l&#x27;Honorable Claude Kumpel Mpasi dans les installations de Cap Congo Agricole Bandundu\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fsocail.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fsocail.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fsocail.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fsocail.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fsocail.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fsocail.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fsocail.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fsocail.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fsocail.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-cap-ink/90 via-cap-ink/40 to-transparent \n                md:bg-gradient-to-r md:from-cap-ink/90 md:via-cap-ink/50 md:to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-6 font-sans text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-white/70 \n                right-6 md:right-12\">Crédit photo © <!-- -->Cap Congo Agricole Bandundu, Kwilu — 03 juillet</div></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 -mt-[100vh] w-full\"><div class=\"flex min-h-screen w-full items-end px-6 pb-24 md:items-center md:px-16 lg:px-24 \n              justify-start md:justify-start\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl text-left\"><div class=\"mb-8 h-1 w-16 bg-cap-yellow \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"></div><h2 class=\"font-unbounded text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight tracking-wide text-white drop-shadow-lg md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Hôpital de Babama</h2><div class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl space-y-4 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 drop-shadow md:mt-8 md:text-2xl \n                  \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><p>Dans le cadre de ses actions communautaires à Babama, la société Cap Congo Agro Palm a procédé à la construction d&#x27;un hôpital afin d&#x27;améliorer l&#x27;accès aux soins de santé pour la population locale.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex min-h-screen w-full items-end px-6 pb-24 md:items-center md:px-16 lg:px-24 \n              justify-start md:justify-end\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl text-left md:text-right\"><div class=\"mb-8 h-1 w-16 bg-cap-yellow md:ml-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"></div><h2 class=\"font-unbounded text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight tracking-wide text-white drop-shadow-lg md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">CS Babama</h2><div class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl space-y-4 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 drop-shadow md:mt-8 md:text-2xl \n                  md:ml-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><p>Le chantier du CS Babama a accueilli la visite du Bourgmestre de Lubunga, un encouragement fort pour notre engagement social.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex min-h-screen w-full items-end px-6 pb-24 md:items-center md:px-16 lg:px-24 \n              justify-start md:justify-start\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl text-left\"><div class=\"mb-8 h-1 w-16 bg-cap-yellow \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"></div><h2 class=\"font-unbounded text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight tracking-wide text-white drop-shadow-lg md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Don de vareuses</h2><div class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl space-y-4 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 drop-shadow md:mt-8 md:text-2xl \n                  \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><p>La société Cap Congo Agro Palm a procédé à un don de vareuses en faveur de la population de Lubunga, témoignant ainsi de son engagement social et de sa proximité avec les communautés locales.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex min-h-screen w-full items-end px-6 pb-24 md:items-center md:px-16 lg:px-24 \n              justify-start md:justify-end\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl text-left md:text-right\"><div class=\"mb-8 h-1 w-16 bg-cap-yellow md:ml-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"></div><h2 class=\"font-unbounded text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight tracking-wide text-white drop-shadow-lg md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Distribution de maïs</h2><div class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl space-y-4 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 drop-shadow md:mt-8 md:text-2xl \n                  md:ml-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><p>Dans le cadre de ses actions communautaires, la Société Cap Congo agricole Bandundu avait organisé une distribution de maïs en faveur de la communauté de Mushie Pentane, contribuant ainsi au soutien alimentaire et au développement des communautés locales.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex min-h-screen w-full items-end px-6 pb-24 md:items-center md:px-16 lg:px-24 \n              justify-start md:justify-start\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl text-left\"><div class=\"mb-8 h-1 w-16 bg-cap-yellow \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"></div><h2 class=\"font-unbounded text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight tracking-wide text-white drop-shadow-lg md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Visite officielle</h2><div class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl space-y-4 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 drop-shadow md:mt-8 md:text-2xl \n                  \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><p>Retour en images de la visite du Président de l&#x27;Assemblée Provinciale du Kwilu, l&#x27;Honorable Claude KUMPEL MPASI, dans les installations de Cap Congo Agricole Bandundu, ce 03 juillet, témoigne de l&#x27;intérêt porté au développement du secteur agricole et à la valorisation des initiatives locales.</p><p>Cette rencontre a permis de présenter notre vision, nos infrastructures ainsi que notre engagement en faveur d&#x27;une agriculture moderne, créatrice d&#x27;emplois et de richesse pour la province du Kwilu et la RDC. Nous remercions chaleureusement l&#x27;Honorable Président pour cette visite et les échanges constructifs autour de l&#x27;avenir de l&#x27;agriculture.</p><p>Ensemble, bâtissons une agriculture forte et durable!</p></div></div></div></div></section></main><section class=\"bg-background pt-10 font-sans md:pt-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-[min(100%,80rem)] px-4 sm:px-6\"><div class=\"relative z-10 -mb-20 md:-mb-24\"><div class=\"group relative h-[min(24rem,75vw)] overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-[0_24px_60px_-12px_rgba(29,29,27,0.25)] sm:h-[22rem] md:h-96\"><img alt=\"Champs — CAP Congo\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover opacity-90 transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-[1.03]\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 80rem\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-cap-forest/90 via-cap-dark-green/70 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center p-6 sm:p-12 md:p-16 lg:p-24\"><h2 class=\"max-w-2xl font-unbounded text-2xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-background sm:text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl\">Produire local, nourrir durablement.</h2></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-full\"><div class=\"rounded-t-3xl bg-cap-ink px-4 pb-12 pt-24 text-background sm:px-10 md:px-12 md:pb-16 md:pt-40\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 border-b border-background/15 pb-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16\"><div class=\"space-y-10\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-start gap-5 sm:flex-row sm:gap-8\"><a class=\"group relative shrink-0 w-fit outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-cap-yellow focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-cap-ink rounded-full\" aria-label=\"CAP Congo — accueil\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"block rounded-full bg-background p-1.5 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.35)] ring-2 ring-cap-green/35 transition group-hover:ring-cap-yellow/60\"><span class=\"relative block size-20 sm:size-24 md:size-28 lg:size-32\"><img alt=\"CAP CONGO SARL\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"